  Title: The Complete Works of Chuang Tzu
  Translator: Burton Watson
Title: The Way Of Heaven
---
Shun said, "Heaven raised on high, earth in peace, sun and moon
shining, the four seasons marching - if you could be like the constant
succession of day and night, the clouds which move, the rains that
fall!"
